---
// LeistungenSection.astro — 4 Cards im 2x2 Grid (neu)
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-28 section-padding bg-transparent" id="leistungen" aria-label="Leistungen">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#0F172A] mb-4">
        Meine <span class="text-[#4D7CFF]">Leistungen</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[#475569] text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Von der ersten Idee bis zum Launch — und darüber hinaus.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1: Website-Erstellung -->
      <article class="leistung-card">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#4D7CFF]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4D7CFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0F172A] mb-3" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">Website-Erstellung</h3>
        <p class="text-[#475569] text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Astro &amp; Drupal. Statisch oder mit CMS — immer DSGVO-konform, immer schnell. Tailwind CSS, responsiv, barrierefrei.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 2: SEO & GEO -->
      <article class="leistung-card">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#4D7CFF]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4D7CFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/>
            <line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/>
            <line x1="11" y1="8" x2="11" y2="14"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="11" x2="14" y2="11"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0F172A] mb-3" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">SEO &amp; GEO</h3>
        <p class="text-[#475569] text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Sichtbar sein, wo Kunden suchen. Klassisches SEO + Optimierung für KI-Suchmaschinen (ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google SGE).
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 3: DSGVO & Security -->
      <article class="leistung-card">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#4D7CFF]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4D7CFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            <polyline points="9 12 12 15 16 10"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0F172A] mb-3" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">DSGVO &amp; Security</h3>
        <p class="text-[#475569] text-sm leading-relaxed">
          DSGVO ist Bauprinzip, nicht Formular. Kein Tracking, keine US-Tools, EU-Hosting. Ihre Daten bleiben in Europa.
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 4: Wartung & Support -->
      <article class="leistung-card">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#4D7CFF]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4D7CFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0F172A] mb-3" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">Wartung &amp; Support</h3>
        <p class="text-[#475569] text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Persönlich, ohne Ticket-System. Updates, Monitoring, Content-Pflege — monatlich oder bei Bedarf.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .leistung-card {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .leistung-card:hover {
    border-color: #4D7CFF;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px -8px rgba(77, 124, 255, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
</style>
